2 (5) A CONVICTION FOR A MISDEMEANOR THAT DID NOT INVOLVE
3 PHYSICAL HARM TO ANOTHER INDIVIDUAL;
4 (6) A CONVICTION FOR WHICH A PERIOD OF 3 YEARS HAS PASSED
